Audit log for all notifications sent to the user. Tracks delivery, interaction, and effectiveness metrics for analytics and debugging.

Remarks

This entity records every notification sent to the user, including:

  • Which article triggered the notification
  • Which rule (if any) generated it
  • Delivery status and any errors
  • User interaction (clicked, dismissed, snoozed)
  • Performance metrics (duration, timing)

Used for:

  • Notification history UI
  • Analytics on notification effectiveness
  • Debugging failed notifications
  • Preventing duplicate notifications

Performance optimizations:

  • Indexed on ArticleId for quick history lookups
  • Indexed on RuleId for rule effectiveness analysis
  • Indexed on SentAt for time-based queries and cleanup
  • MaxLength constraints on text fields to optimize storage
